================================================================================
SnakeGame-C - Professional Snake Game Implementation
================================================================================

This software is a professionally crafted Snake game implementation featuring:

- Advanced C++17 programming techniques
- Modern graphics rendering with SDL2
- Professional audio system with real-time synthesis
- Particle physics simulation
- Multi-state game architecture
- Cross-platform compatibility

Developed with industry-standard practices including:
- RAII resource management
- Exception safety
- Performance optimization
- Professional documentation
- Comprehensive error handling

For more information, see README.md